  "title": "Sales Support Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle pre-sales enquiries on product availability, lead time, and pricing</p></li><li><p>Assist with sales order processing and order amendments</p></li><li><p>Support new item and customer setup in the system</p></li><li><p>Track orders and update customers on delivery status</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with factories, warehouses, and forwarders for shipments</p></li><li><p>Prepare invoices, shipping documents, and maintain proper filing</p></li><li><p>Support internal teams and customers with timely communication</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Good communication and basic customer service skills</p></li><li><p>Computer literate and detail-oriented</p></li><li><p>Responsible, reliable, and a strong team player</p></li><li><p>Willing to learn and open to development opportunities</p></li><li><p>Oracle system experience is an advantage</p></li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please send your updated CV in MS Word format to<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">candy.lim@peopleprofilers.com</a></p><p>All applications will be treated in strict confidence.</p><p>People Profilers Pte Ltd<br />DID: 6950 9738<br /><a href=\"http://www.peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://www.peopleprofilers.com</a></p><p>Lim Yi Tian, Candy<br />EA License No. 02C4944<br />Registration No. R1109829</p>",
